@startuml
title TPL Architecture - System Context

left to right direction
skinparam shadowing false

actor "Coordinator / Physician / Admin" as User
rectangle "TPL Application" as TPL
database "SQLite / DB Backend" as DB
cloud "Browser Runtime" as Browser

User --> Browser : interacts
Browser --> TPL : uses via HTTP API
TPL --> DB : persists and queries

@enduml
